QuestData.Title: Those Aren't Fish Eggs
QuestData.Description: Corruption has seeped into the sea.$b$bPart of our job is to keep the monsters of these parts under control. A cruel magic has taken over many of the beasts. I take the challenge of the hunt with pride, but too many and we are overrun!$b$bMonster eggs are scattered across the breeding grounds, pulsing with a dark energy.$b$bGet your stompin' boots on.
QuestData.LogDescription: Break $1oa Corrupted Eggs in Krakenbane Cove.
QuestData.CompletionText: Ah, the satisfying squish of a monster egg under your boot. What a feeling!
QuestData.RewardText: It's best to not know what corrupted eggs will hatch into, though I could imagine the fight that we may now never see.
